description: Bull Head Barbecue Sauce, also known as Shacha Sauce, is a popular sauce from Taiwan that is made with a mix of dried fish, dried shrimps and various spices. It can be used as a stir-fry sauce, hot pot condiment or as a marinade for grill meat to add a remarkable umami smoky flavour.
name: Barbecue Sauce
